---
title: Figgy Balsamic Pork Cutlets with Roasted Carrots & Rosemary Potatoes
description: You’ve likely come across figs baked into desserts, nestled onto cheese platters, or preserved and slathered on toast for breakfast. But today, we’re mixing it up by pairing fig jam with tangy balsamic vinegar. The result? A sweet and savory sauce that when drizzled on pork cutlets elevates them to extra-special status. Roasted carrots and rosemary potatoes complete the company-worthy meal.
